---
name: perf-takehome-kernel-opt-fast
version: 1
schema: omhflow/v1
models:
  roles:
    implementer: infini/gpt-5.5:xhigh
    repair: infini/gpt-5.5:xhigh
    reviewer: infini/claude-opus-4-8:high
  defaults:
    agent: implementer
    review: reviewer
  unavailable: fail
checkpoint:
  stopDeadlineMs: 300000
changePolicy:
  agentsCanPropose: true
  humansCanApprove: true
---
# Perf Take-home Kernel Optimization — FAST (2 LLM calls/round: implement + review)

Single-task, minimal loop. Each round: one implementer (gpt-5.5:xhigh) directly edits
`perf_takehome.py`, one reviewer (opus-4-8:high) confirms compliance (correctness + no
reward-hack) AND proposes the next optimization. Script nodes enforce hard limits
(protected files, correctness/cycle validation, git checkpoint). No coordinator, no plan
review loop, no separate strategy node.

```yaml workflow
stateSchema:
  version: 1
  shape:
    campaign: object
    protectedFiles: object
    leaderboard: object
    selection: object
    taskContext: object
    implementation: object
    implementationPrecheck: object
    validation: object
    /validation/status: string
    /validation/repair_exhausted: boolean
    rewardHackReview: object
    performanceReview: object
    revision: object
    taskBestUpdate: object
    leaderboardUpdate: object
    /campaign/pause: object
    /campaign/continue: boolean
    /localLoop: object
    /localLoop/continueSameTask: boolean
    /campaign/forcedTaskDir: string
resources:
  - path: scripts/lane-utils.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/run-js-workflow-script.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/preflight-campaign.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/protected-files-baseline.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/protected-files-check.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/load-campaign-state.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/select-forced-task-workload.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/compact-task-context.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/implementation-precheck.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/validate-kernel.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/derive-review-verdicts.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/record-task-best.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/promote-and-update-leaderboard.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/task-local-loop-gate.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/next-task-or-finalize.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/git-round-checkpoint.js
    kind: script
  - path: scripts/time-budget-gate.js
    kind: script
  - path: prompts/fast-implement.md
    kind: prompt
  - path: prompts/correctness-repair.md
    kind: prompt
  - path: prompts/fast-review.md
    kind: prompt
capabilities:
  tools:
    - bash
    - eval
    - task
  agents:
    - task
    - reviewer
nodes:
  - id: preflightCampaign
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/preflight-campaign.js
    writes:
      - /campaign
  - id: protectedFilesBaseline
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/protected-files-baseline.js
    reads:
      - /campaign
    writes:
      - /protectedFiles
  - id: loadCampaignState
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/load-campaign-state.js
    reads:
      - /campaign
      - /localLoop
    writes:
      - /campaign
      - /leaderboard
  - id: selectForcedTaskWorkload
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/select-forced-task-workload.js
    reads:
      - /campaign
      - /leaderboard
    writes:
      - /selection
  - id: compactTaskContext
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/compact-task-context.js
    reads:
      - /selection
      - /campaign
      - /localLoop
      - /performanceReview
      - /validation
      - /revision
      - /taskContext
    writes:
      - /taskContext
  - id: implementCandidate
    type: agent
    agent: task
    model:
      role: implementer
    reads:
      - /taskContext
    prompt:
      template:
        file: prompts/fast-implement.md
        bindings:
          taskContext:
            state: /taskContext
          implementationStatePath:
            inline: /implementation
    writes:
      - /implementation
  - id: implementationPrecheck
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/implementation-precheck.js
    reads:
      - /taskContext
      - /implementation
    writes:
      - /implementationPrecheck
  - id: protectedFilesCheckImplementation
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/protected-files-check.js
    reads:
      - /taskContext
      - /implementationPrecheck
      - /protectedFiles
    writes:
      - /protectedFiles
  - id: validateKernel
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      timeoutMs: 3600000
      file: scripts/validate-kernel.js
    reads:
      - /taskContext
      - /implementationPrecheck
    writes:
      - /validation
  - id: localCorrectnessRepair
    type: agent
    agent: task
    model:
      role: repair
    reads:
      - /taskContext
      - /validation
    prompt:
      template:
        file: prompts/correctness-repair.md
        bindings:
          taskContext:
            state: /taskContext
          validation:
            state: /validation
          implementationStatePath:
            inline: /implementation
    writes:
      - /implementation
  - id: reviewCandidate
    type: agent
    agent: task
    model:
      role: reviewer
    workspaceAccess: read
    reads:
      - /taskContext
      - /implementationPrecheck
      - /validation
      - /leaderboard
    prompt:
      template:
        file: prompts/fast-review.md
        bindings:
          taskContext:
            state: /taskContext
          precheck:
            state: /implementationPrecheck
          validation:
            state: /validation
          leaderboard:
            state: /leaderboard
          performanceReviewStatePath:
            inline: /performanceReview
    writes:
      - /performanceReview
  - id: deriveReviewVerdicts
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/derive-review-verdicts.js
    reads:
      - /performanceReview
    writes:
      - /rewardHackReview
  - id: recordTaskBest
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/record-task-best.js
    reads:
      - /taskContext
      - /validation
      - /rewardHackReview
      - /performanceReview
    writes:
      - /taskBestUpdate
  - id: promoteAndUpdateLeaderboard
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/promote-and-update-leaderboard.js
    reads:
      - /taskContext
      - /validation
      - /rewardHackReview
      - /performanceReview
    writes:
      - /leaderboard
      - /leaderboardUpdate
  - id: taskLocalLoopGate
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/task-local-loop-gate.js
    reads:
      - /campaign
      - /taskContext
      - /validation
      - /rewardHackReview
      - /performanceReview
      - /leaderboardUpdate
      - /localLoop
    writes:
      - /campaign
      - /localLoop
  - id: nextTaskOrFinalize
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/next-task-or-finalize.js
    reads:
      - /campaign
      - /leaderboard
    writes:
      - /campaign
  - id: gitRoundCheckpoint
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/git-round-checkpoint.js
    reads:
      - /campaign
      - /taskContext
      - /validation
      - /leaderboardUpdate
    writes:
      - /campaign
  - id: timeBudgetGate
    type: script
    script:
      language: js
      file: scripts/time-budget-gate.js
    reads:
      - /campaign
    writes:
      - /campaign
edges:
  - from: preflightCampaign
    to: protectedFilesBaseline
  - from: protectedFilesBaseline
    to: loadCampaignState
  - from: loadCampaignState
    to: selectForcedTaskWorkload
  - from: selectForcedTaskWorkload
    to: compactTaskContext
  - from: compactTaskContext
    to: implementCandidate
  - from: implementCandidate
    to: implementationPrecheck
  - from: implementationPrecheck
    to: protectedFilesCheckImplementation
  - from: protectedFilesCheckImplementation
    to: validateKernel
  - from: validateKernel
    to: localCorrectnessRepair
    when: state.validation.status != "passed" && state.validation.repair_exhausted != true
  - from: localCorrectnessRepair
    to: implementationPrecheck
  - from: validateKernel
    to: reviewCandidate
    when: state.validation.status == "passed"
  # Escape hatch: if correctness repair is exhausted, do NOT loop on repair again. Fall through to
  # review; taskLocalLoopGate will park/replan instead of a tight repair loop.
  - from: validateKernel
    to: reviewCandidate
    when: state.validation.status != "passed" && state.validation.repair_exhausted == true
  - from: reviewCandidate
    to: deriveReviewVerdicts
  - from: deriveReviewVerdicts
    to: recordTaskBest
  - from: recordTaskBest
    to: promoteAndUpdateLeaderboard
  - from: promoteAndUpdateLeaderboard
    to: taskLocalLoopGate
  - from: taskLocalLoopGate
    to: nextTaskOrFinalize
    when: state.localLoop.continueSameTask != true
  - from: taskLocalLoopGate
    to: gitRoundCheckpoint
    when: state.localLoop.continueSameTask == true
  - from: nextTaskOrFinalize
    to: gitRoundCheckpoint
  - from: gitRoundCheckpoint
    to: timeBudgetGate
  - from: timeBudgetGate
    to: compactTaskContext
    when: state.campaign.continue == true && state.localLoop.continueSameTask == true
  - from: timeBudgetGate
    to: loadCampaignState
    when: state.campaign.continue == true && state.localLoop.continueSameTask != true
```
